headline: Match Group (MTCH) Long-Term Estimates Reduced by TD Cowen
summary: Match Group Inc. (NASDAQ:MTCH) is one of the most undervalued mid cap stocks to buy now. On February 4, TD Cowen lowered its price target on Match Group to $37 from $40 with a Buy rating following solid Q4 2025 results.
